OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will
OL,6,Fremain cloudy through the evening and
OL,7,Fovernight with some showery outbreaks
OL,8,Fof rain, some of these will be heavy
OL,9,Fat first, gradually easing overnight.
OL,10,
OL,11,CSunday:FDull and cloudy with some
OL,12,Flight rain in the morning. Some
OL,13,Fbrighter spells may develop later.
OL,14,FChance of a heavy shower in the
OL,15,Fsouthwest. Feeling cool in the east.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
